{"tid":2366662,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"民政局政助黎穎瑜因BNO辭職？消息指謠傳：赴新加坡照顧夫兒","createTime":"2021-01-14T16:29:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T03:19:48.000Z","uid":60281,"like":7,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"9bdf52c97e61f9090cfa6c9d12bcb687da4d917f","tid":2366662,"uid":60281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T16:29:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今月底英國將開始接受持BNO護照港人以「5+1」方式申請移民英國，而近日就有媒體引述消息指，中央將對英國BNO放權政策提反制措施，包括禁止持BNO人士在港擔任公職及投票。今晚黎穎瑜請辭消息曝光後，網上有猜測她是為了BNO原因。不過知情人士向《香港01》表示，有關猜測非事實，黎穎瑜並無持有BNO。<br />\n<br />\n該人士表示，黎穎瑜丈夫在新加坡土生土長，與黎結婚後移居香港有18之久，現打算返回新加坡。黎為照顧丈夫和兒子，選擇辭職，一同赴新加坡居住。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/政情/574676/民政局政助黎穎瑜因bno辭職-消息指謠傳-赴新加坡照顧夫兒</code></pre>"},{"pid":"e3e7e10ccfa4fbb9ba54b2f4e024d5114cbc8708","tid":2366662,"uid":56432,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T16:29:52.000Z","msg":"點解唔去大灣區啊⋯⋯"},{"pid":"264f3d4bae975fe832f101df46dbf26daf8d9980","tid":2366662,"uid":2054,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T16:30:15.000Z","msg":"明啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6793b9c5cb1621a987404fb53783d33574b151a4","tid":2366662,"uid":255980,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T16:30:20.000Z","msg":"Mon po狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f9e61d3dd65a5bcaf4c94db2af7115628405ee8","tid":2366662,"uid":224066,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T16:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/XjaraFAI4zjR2ap3Imjyj14zEoY=/1950x1097/fi